  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the grant is to finance part of the expenses for an actual secretariat for Solutions Alliance. The secretariat will be responsible for reporting, coordination and administration on behalf of The Chair of the Solutions Alliance. The tasks will, among other things, include the preparation of meetings, advocacy and coordination support for thematic and national groups.

A separate purpose of the grant is to finance a special edition of Refugee Studies Centres magazine Forced Migration Review (FMR), that with a focus on durable solutions to refugee crises will be published in a collaboration with Solutions Alliance.</narrative>
